--- title: "Cotação do ouro - Parte 4 " subtitle: "Modelos exp_smoothing" author: "Pedro Lima" date: "2023-08-05" categories: [Modelagem, Série-Temporal,R] toc: true toc-depth: 3 draft: false --- ::: {.cell} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_a76af237a2ee277a9fa1f2bb8a0cf36e'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_da42cf6586779db4fc129bf9135930a1'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_f9fad3151b2cd81cbee3812016d570a7'} ```{.r .cell-code} splits <- gold_mean %>% time_series_split( assess = "1 year", cumulative = TRUE ) cv <- gold_mean %>% time_series_cv( assess = 12 * 0.5, initial = 12 * 4, skip = 12 * 1, slice_limit = 6, culmulatime = FALSE ) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_4cdeb89aaa059f3e18180c67f3e11235'} ```{.r .cell-code} splits %>% tk_time_series_cv_plan() %>% plot_time_series_cv_plan(mes,media, .facet_ncol = 1, .interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-6_f350fa8c0345e5ac75da9bb3e6384729'} ```{.r .cell-code} cv %>% tk_time_series_cv_plan() %>% plot_time_series_cv_plan(mes,media, .facet_ncol = 2, .interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ## Modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-7_6dd8ad85589064e5c0257a9f2686d21a'} ```{.r .cell-code} exp_ets <- exp_smoothing( seasonal_period = 12, error = "multiplicative", trend = "additive", season = "multiplicative" ) %>% set_engine("ets") %>% fit(media ~ mes, training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-8_945149029bd281e5dde8e95273d77e33'} ```{.r .cell-code} exp_croston <- exp_smoothing( smooth_level = 0.2 ) %>% set_engine("croston") %>% fit(media ~ mes, training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-9_cdcce5b116dc21f5c288c31717a0d944'} ```{.r .cell-code} exp_theta <- exp_smoothing() %>% set_engine("theta") %>% fit(media ~ mes, training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-10_86297484306fc8698450873e1fde53d7'} ```{.r .cell-code} exp_smooth <- exp_smoothing( seasonal_period = 12, error = "multiplicative", trend = "additive_damped", season = "additive" ) %>% set_engine("smooth_es") %>% fit(media ~ mes, training(splits)) ``` ::: ## Comparando os modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-11_d9b3a8bf4d1f1eecad1c0ca0d33bf45a'} ```{.r .cell-code} model_table <- modeltime_table( exp_ets, exp_croston, exp_theta, exp_smooth ) ``` ::: ## Calibrando ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-12_b75366c7a7330123e37357feabd0218b'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table <- model_table %>% modeltime_calibrate(testing(splits)) ``` ::: ## Residual ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-13_c3a10c01482f8ae4b5bf79e1309eecbd'} ```{.r .cell-code} # calib_table %>% # modeltime_residuals() %>% # plot_modeltime_residuals( # .type = "seasonality", # .interactive = FALSE # ) ``` ::: ## Accuracy ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-14_f7614a1f35d2a7faa6eaee8fd6e37508'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_accuracy() ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # A tibble: 4 × 9 .model_id .model_desc .type mae mape mase smape rmse rsq 1 1 ETS(M,A,M) Test 22.9 12.8 5.02 13.8 24.8 0.0431 2 2 CROSTON METHOD Test 11.1 6.27 2.44 6.45 12.2 NA 3 3 THETA METHOD Test 17.3 9.68 3.81 10.3 19.1 0.582 4 4 ETS(MADA) Test 25.5 14.3 5.60 15.6 27.3 0.115 ``` ::: ::: ## Test set visualization ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-15_644b3f1a79ec2dbb183907fcd38e2bd7'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_forecast( new_data = testing(splits), actual_data = gold_mean ) %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ## Validação Cruzada ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-16_257d643eae6a10a79967dcabb27ef690'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted <- model_table %>% modeltime_fit_resamples( resamples = cv, control = control_resamples(verbose = FALSE) ) resamples_fitted ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # Modeltime Table # A tibble: 4 × 4 .model_id .model .model_desc .resample_results 1 1 ETS(M,A,M) 2 2 CROSTON METHOD 3 3 THETA METHOD 4 4 ETS(MADA) ``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-17_94e6fe3a8deb54257b760d365c5e39a1'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% plot_modeltime_resamples( .point_size = 3, .point_alpha = 0.8, .interactive = FALSE ) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-17-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-18_d11360c61c6716f19fe9608660f97cac'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% modeltime_resample_accuracy(summary_fns = mean) %>% table_modeltime_accuracy(.interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}

``` ::: ::: ## Forecast future ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-19_17495263b7bb9d4fbbfa4886ea1bc840'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl <- calib_table %>% modeltime_refit(gold_mean) %>% modeltime_forecast( h = "1 year", actual_data = gold_mean ) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-20_809f60008b7b5ba67e9771825e739683'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
